+# Twitter Auto X
+
+Phase1 starter for the Twitter（X）自動投稿システム.
+
+## Setup
+
+```bash
+npm install
+npm run dev
+```
+
+Open http://localhost:3000 to confirm the app displays **Setup OK**.
+
+## Environment Variables
+
+Copy `.env.example` to `.env.local` and fill in your Supabase credentials.
